description: A lightweight easy-to-use library for persisting settings using different backing storage implementations. This library contains implementations using an XML file or the Registry as the backing storage. The source code on Bitbucket also contains experimental but fully working implementations that use Azure Tables and SQL Server as the backing storage.
releaseNotes: Remove useless xml file from package (Bitbucket Issue #18). No code logic changes.
summary: A lightweight library for persisting settings.
